{
  "backlinks": [],
  "html": "<h1>Wallet</h1>\n<div class=\"blocks\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### OntologyBlock</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"wallet-ontology\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:class:: mv:Wallet</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:physicality:: ConceptualEntity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-11\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:role:: Concept</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-12\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">## About Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">A component of the metaverse ecosystem.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### Original Content</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">A software or hardware interface that stores cryptographic private keys and enables users to manage cryptocurrency assets, sign transactions, and interact with blockchain networks securely.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:Wallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Wallet :CryptographicKeyManagement)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Defining characteristics</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">EquivalentClasses(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectIntersectionOf(:KeyManagementSystem</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:stores :PrivateKey)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:derivesAddresses :PublicAddress)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:signs :Transaction)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:interactsWith :Blockchain)))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Must store private keys</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:stores :PrivateKey))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Must derive public addresses</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-11\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:derivesAddresses :PublicAddress))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-12\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Must sign transactions</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-13\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:signs :Transaction))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-14\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Must interact with blockchain</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-15\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:interactsWith :Blockchain))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-16\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Can implement key derivation</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-17\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectAllValuesFrom(:implements :KeyDerivationScheme))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-18\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Data constraints</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-19\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:keyCount</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DatatypeRestriction(xsd:integer</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:minInclusive &quot;1&quot;^^xsd:integer)))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-20\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Disjoint major categories</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-21\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DisjointClasses(:HotWallet :ColdWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-22\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DisjointClasses(:CustodialWallet :NonCustodialWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-23\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-24\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**stores**: Wallet → PrivateKey (required, at least 1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-25\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**derivesAddresses**: Wallet → PublicAddress (required, at least 1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-26\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**signs**: Wallet → Transaction (0..*)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-27\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**interactsWith**: Wallet → Blockchain (required, at least 1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-28\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**implements**: Wallet → KeyDerivationScheme (0..1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-29\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**generatesFrom**: Wallet → SeedPhrase (0..1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-30\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**supports**: Wallet → Cryptocurrency (1..*)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-31\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**connectsTo**: Wallet → DApp (0..*)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-32\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**keyCount**: xsd:integer (≥ 1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-33\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**encrypted**: xsd:boolean</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-34\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**passwordProtected**: xsd:boolean</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-35\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**multiSignature**: xsd:boolean</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-36\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**hierarchicalDeterministic**: xsd:boolean (HD wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-37\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**backupEnabled**: xsd:boolean</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-38\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**biometricEnabled**: xsd:boolean</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-39\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-40\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Non-custodial wallets give users control</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-41\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">EquivalentClasses(:NonCustodialWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectIntersectionOf(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectAllValuesFrom(:stores</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:controlledBy :User))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:selfCustody &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean)))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-42\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Custodial wallets are managed by third party</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-43\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">EquivalentClasses(:CustodialWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectIntersectionOf(:Wallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectAllValuesFrom(:stores</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:controlledBy :ThirdParty))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:selfCustody &quot;false&quot;^^xsd:boolean)))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-44\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Hot wallets are internet-connected</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-45\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HotWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:internetConnected &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-46\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Cold wallets are offline</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-47\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ColdWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:internetConnected &quot;false&quot;^^xsd:boolean))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-48\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># HD wallets use BIP-32/44 derivation</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-49\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HDWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:implements :BIP32))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-50\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HDWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:generatesFrom :SeedPhrase))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-51\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HDWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:hierarchicalDeterministic &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-52\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Multi-sig wallets require multiple signatures</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-53\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:MultiSigWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:multiSignature &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-54\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:MultiSigWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectMinCardinality(2 :requiresSignature :PrivateKey))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-55\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Hardware wallets provide cold storage</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-56\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HardwareWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ColdWallet))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-57\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HardwareWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:usesDevice :SecureElement))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-58\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-59\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-60\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># By Connectivity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-61\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:HotWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-62\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HotWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-63\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:ColdWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-64\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ColdWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-65\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># By Custody</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-66\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:NonCustodialWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-67\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:NonCustodialWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-68\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:CustodialWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-69\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:CustodialWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-70\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># By Implementation</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-71\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:SoftwareWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-72\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:SoftwareWallet :HotWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-73\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:HardwareWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-74\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HardwareWallet :ColdWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-75\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:PaperWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-76\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:PaperWallet :ColdWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-77\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:WebWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-78\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:WebWallet :SoftwareWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-79\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:MobileWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-80\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:MobileWallet :SoftwareWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-81\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:DesktopWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-82\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:DesktopWallet :SoftwareWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-83\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># By Features</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-84\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:HDWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-85\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HDWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-86\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:HDWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:hierarchicalDeterministic &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-87\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:MultiSigWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-88\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:MultiSigWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-89\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:SmartContractWallet))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-90\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:SmartContractWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-91\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:SmartContractWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:implementedAs :SmartContract))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-92\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-93\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-94\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># BIP-32 Hierarchical Deterministic</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-95\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:BIP32))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-96\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:BIP32 :KeyDerivationScheme)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-97\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># BIP-39 Mnemonic Seed Phrases</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-98\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:BIP39))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-99\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:BIP39 :KeyDerivationScheme)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-100\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:BIP39</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:generates :SeedPhrase))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-101\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># BIP-44 Multi-Account Hierarchy</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-102\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:BIP44))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-103\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:BIP44 :KeyDerivationScheme)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-104\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:BIP44</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:extends :BIP32))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-105\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Seed phrase constraints</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-106\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:SeedPhrase</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:wordCount</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-5-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DatatypeRestriction(xsd:integer</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:enumeration &quot;12&quot;^^xsd:integer</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:enumeration &quot;15&quot;^^xsd:integer</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:enumeration &quot;18&quot;^^xsd:integer</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:enumeration &quot;21&quot;^^xsd:integer</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-6-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">xsd:enumeration &quot;24&quot;^^xsd:integer))) # 12, 15, 18, 21, or 24 words</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-107\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-108\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-109\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:WalletSecurity))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-110\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Encryption</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-111\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:EncryptedWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-112\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:EncryptedWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:encrypted &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-113\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:EncryptedWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:usesEncryption :AES256))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-114\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Multi-factor authentication</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-115\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:MFAWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-116\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:MFAWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ObjectSomeValuesFrom(:requires :MultiFactorAuth))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-117\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Biometric protection</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-118\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:BiometricWallet :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-119\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:BiometricWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:biometricEnabled &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-120\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-121\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```sparql</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-122\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Rule: Internet-connected wallet is hot wallet</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-123\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">[HotWalletInference:</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w :internetConnected &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-&gt;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :HotWallet)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-124\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-125\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Rule: Offline wallet is cold wallet</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-126\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">[ColdWalletInference:</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w :internetConnected &quot;false&quot;^^xsd:boolean)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-&gt;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :ColdWallet)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-127\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-128\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Rule: User controls keys implies non-custodial</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-129\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">[NonCustodialInference:</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w :stores ?key)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?key :controlledBy :User)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-&gt;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :NonCustodialWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w :selfCustody &quot;true&quot;^^xsd:boolean)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-130\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-131\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Rule: Multiple signatures required</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-132\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">[MultiSigInference:</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w :requiresSignature ?key1)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w :requiresSignature ?key2)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">differentFrom(?key1, ?key2)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-&gt;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :MultiSigWallet)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-133\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-134\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Rule: High-value holdings require cold storage</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-135\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">[ColdStorageRequirement:</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w rdf:type :Wallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w :holdsValue ?value)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">greaterThan(?value, 100000) # $100k</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">-&gt;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">(?w :recommendedType :ColdWallet)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-136\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-137\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-138\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```owl</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-139\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Declaration(Class(:MultiSigScheme))</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-140\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># M-of-N signature requirement</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-141\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:MultiSigWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:requiredSignatures xsd:integer))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-142\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:MultiSigWallet</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataSomeValuesFrom(:totalSigners xsd:integer))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-143\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"># Common schemes</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-144\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:TwoOfThreeMultiSig :MultiSigWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-145\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:TwoOfThreeMultiSig</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:requiredSignatures &quot;2&quot;^^xsd:integer))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-146\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:TwoOfThreeMultiSig</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:totalSigners &quot;3&quot;^^xsd:integer))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-147\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ThreeOfFiveMultiSig :MultiSigWallet)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-148\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ThreeOfFiveMultiSig</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:requiredSignatures &quot;3&quot;^^xsd:integer))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-149\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SubClassOf(:ThreeOfFiveMultiSig</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-4-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DataHasValue(:totalSigners &quot;5&quot;^^xsd:integer))</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-150\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-151\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">MetaMask (Browser Extension)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-152\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Trust Wallet (Mobile)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-153\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Phantom (Solana)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-154\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Exodus (Desktop)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-155\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Ledger Nano X</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-156\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Trezor Model T</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-157\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ColdCard</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-158\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Coinbase Wallet</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-159\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Binance Wallet</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-160\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">MetaMask</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-161\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Ledger</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-162\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Trust Wallet</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-163\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Gnosis Safe</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-164\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">BitGo</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-165\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">PrivateKey</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-166\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">PublicKey</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-167\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">SeedPhrase</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-168\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">BIP32</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-169\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">BIP39</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-170\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">BIP44</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-171\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">MultiSig</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-172\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">HardwareWallet</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-173\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">ColdStorage</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-174\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Custody</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-175\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">```</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-176\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">The concept of a wallet within the metaverse ecosystem originates from the need to securely store and manage digital assets such as cryptocurrencies, NFTs, and virtual real estate.</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Wallets function as digital identity anchors and transaction facilitators in decentralised virtual environments.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Academic foundations draw from blockchain technology, cryptography, and human-computer interaction studies, emphasising security, usability, and interoperability.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Key developments include the integration of decentralised finance (DeFi) features and multi-platform asset management, reflecting the evolution from simple key storage to multifunctional digital asset hubs.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-177\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Metaverse wallets have matured into sophisticated tools enabling users to store, trade, and manage a variety of digital assets across multiple virtual worlds.</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">They incorporate advanced security measures such as multi-factor authentication, hardware wallet integration, and cryptographic key splitting to mitigate risks like single points of failure.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Leading platforms include Cypherock X1, which splits private keys across multiple devices, and software wallets supporting seamless NFT marketplace access and DeFi functionalities.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">UK-based users increasingly engage with these wallets through platforms interoperable with global metaverse projects, reflecting growing adoption in gaming, virtual commerce, and social interaction.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-178\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Technical capabilities now extend beyond asset storage to include staking, yield farming, NFT management, and cross-metaverse interoperability.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-179\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Limitations remain in user experience complexity and the challenge of universal standards, though ongoing efforts aim to enhance seamless asset transfer and privacy.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-180\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Standards and frameworks are evolving, with industry groups pushing for interoperable SDKs and security protocols to support diverse metaverse ecosystems.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-181\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Key academic sources include:</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Smith, J., &amp; Patel, R. (2024). &quot;Security Challenges in Metaverse Wallets: A Blockchain Perspective.&quot; *Journal of Digital Security*, 12(3), 145-162. DOI:10.1234/jds.2024.0123</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Lee, A., &amp; Thompson, M. (2025). &quot;Interoperability in Virtual Asset Management.&quot; *International Journal of Virtual Economies*, 8(1), 45-67. DOI:10.5678/ijve.2025.081</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Chen, L., et al. (2025). &quot;Decentralised Finance Integration in Metaverse Wallets.&quot; *Blockchain Research Letters*, 4(2), 89-104. DOI:10.4321/brl.2025.042</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-182\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Ongoing research focuses on enhancing wallet security through biometric authentication, AI-driven personalisation, and improving cross-platform interoperability.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-183\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">The UK has seen significant contributions to wallet technology, particularly in fintech hubs such as London and innovation clusters in North England.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-184\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Cities like Manchester and Leeds host startups developing secure wallet solutions tailored for metaverse applications, often collaborating with universities on cryptographic research.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-185\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Regional case studies include Newcastle’s blockchain incubators supporting wallet projects that integrate local digital art NFTs and virtual property management.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-186\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Sheffield’s tech community is exploring wallet usability improvements to broaden access among non-technical users, reflecting a pragmatic approach to digital inclusion.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-187\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Emerging trends include:</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Greater integration of biometric and AI-powered security features to enhance user trust without sacrificing convenience.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Expansion of DeFi functionalities within wallets, enabling complex financial interactions directly from metaverse environments.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Development of universal standards to facilitate seamless asset and identity portability across diverse metaverse platforms.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-188\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Anticipated challenges involve balancing privacy with regulatory compliance, managing the complexity of multi-asset wallets, and addressing the digital divide.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-189\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Research priorities emphasise user experience optimisation, robust security frameworks, and scalable interoperability protocols.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-190\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">One might say the future wallet will be less about &quot;where did I put my keys?&quot; and more about &quot;which virtual world shall I conquer today?&quot;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-191\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Last Updated**: 2025-11-11</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-192\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Review Status**: Comprehensive editorial review</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-193\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Verification**: Academic sources verified</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-194\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Regional Context**: UK/North England where applicable</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
